  "description": "This mod will start to corrupt your world once the Corrupted Block is placed.",
  "body": "<p>Welcome to Null Corruption!</p>\n<p>Null Corruption is my old corruption experiment mod, pretty laggy and mostly here for Archival purposes but feel free to play around with it!</p>\n<p>This mod will start to&nbsp;corrupt your world once the Corrupted Block is placed.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/creraces\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3.2.0/assets/cozy/donate/patreon-singular_vector.svg\" alt=\"Donate\" width=\"186\" height=\"56\" /></a> <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/forge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Available for Forge\" width=\"186\" height=\"56\" /> <a href=\"https://discord.gg//jwAeWYyGug\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-plural_vector.svg\" alt=\"Join the Discord\" width=\"186\" height=\"56\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong><i>Good to know:</i></strong></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><i>1. The Corrupted Block has a small chance of spawning a&nbsp;Corrupted Plant on top of them which will start summoning&nbsp;Corrupted Entities.</i></p>\n<p><i>2. Use the \"/corruption\" command to set the&nbsp;corruption speed.</i></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Known bugs:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><em>N/A</em></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Supported Versions:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><i><strong>1.7.10:</strong>&nbsp;N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.12.2:</strong> LTS: <em>\"Long Term Support\"</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.14.4:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.15.2:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.16.5: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.17.1: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.18.2:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong> 1.19.2:</strong><em> N/A:&nbsp;None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.19.4:</strong><em> N/A:&nbsp;None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><em>Do note that this is the plan but things may change overtime!</em></i></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><strong>FAQ:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>1. How do I get it? - It's creative only meaning you'll need to manually spawn the first block.</p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Credits:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><em><strong>Developers:</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3&nbsp;\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><em>Textures:</em></strong></p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></em></p>\n<p><em><br /><strong>Ideas:</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3&nbsp;\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></strong></em></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<p>Made by: <a title=\"mc_jojo3\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></p>",
